{# One description section per submission, rendered from submissions.toml metadata and
   injected as markdown between the page's descriptions markers (see leaderboard.build_track).
   The heading carries an attr_list id (#model-<key>) — the anchor a submission's name links
   to from the table; keep it in sync with model_link. The shared Jinja env autoescapes for the
   HTML table snippet, so this markdown template opts out: escaping '&'/'<'/quotes would corrupt
   the markdown. Safe here — submissions.toml only changes through reviewed PRs. #}
{% autoescape false %}
{% for s in submissions %}
### {{ s.label }} { #model-{{ s.key }} }

{{ s.description }}

**Authors:** {{ s.authors }} ({{ s.year }}) · **Step units:** {{ s.step_units }} · [Checkpoint]({{ s.url }})
{: .dlb-submission-meta }
{% endfor %}
{% endautoescape %}
